data.description: Soak in the Lowcountry lifestyle in Battery Point! This 3 bdrm, 2½ bath Southern home has deep porches across the front & back, pine floors, lush landscaping, lots of natural light, a open floor plan for entertaining, 2 fireplaces w/ custom built-ins, lots of storage & a owner's suite on the main floor. Battery Point is a waterfront Lowcountry in a natural setting drenched in large oaks & native landscaping. Amenities include a gated swimming pool, clubhouse, tennis court & boat storage area. Picnic areas, fishing, community boat dock & boat launch complete the landscape. Don't miss your opportunity to live in this sought after community.
